#=======================#
#      WH-Questions     #
#=======================#

# 1
Source: a:136
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena: wh questions
ang la are a be
ang la   are             a   be
who FACT stand.STAT.PERF DEF there
'who is standing there?'

# 2
Source: a:136
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena: wh questions
ang-mine la are a be?
ang-mine la   are             a   be
who-pl   FACT stand.STAT.PERF DEF there
'who are standing there?'

# 3
# Adapted from a:136
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: wh questions
bonso ka o are a be?
bonso ka   o    are             a   be
why   that s/he stand.STAT.PERF DEF there
'why is s/he standing there?'

# 4
Source: a:136
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena: wh questions
noba bawola la are a be?
no-ba     ba-wola      la   are             a   be
person-pl pl-how.many  FACT stand.STAT.PERF DEF there
'How many people are standing there?'

# 5
Source: a:135
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena: wh questions
bong la ka o de wa ne?
bong la   ka   o    de        wa        ne?
what FACT that s/he take.PERF come.PERF we
'what did s/he bring?'

# 6
# Adapted from a:135
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: wh questions
boo la ka o de wa ne?
boo       la   ka   o    de        wa        ne?
which.one FACT that s/he take.PERF come.PERF we
'which of them did s/he bring?'

# 7
# Adapted from a:135
# Animate form
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: wh questions
baboo la ka o de wa ne?
baboo    la   ka   o    de        wa        ne?
which.AN FACT that s/he take.PERF come.PERF we
'which did s/he bring?'

# 8
# Adapted from a:135
# Inanimate form
Source: author
Vetted: f
Judgment: g
Phenomena: wh questions
aboo la ka o de wa ne?
aboo       la   ka   o    de        wa        ne?
which.INAN FACT that s/he take.PERF come.PERF we
'which did s/he bring?'

# 9
Source: a:136
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena: wh questions
daboo la ka o wa kyɛ
daboo la   ka   o        wa        kyɛ
when  FACT that s/he.NOM come.PERF here
'when did s/he come here?'

# 10
Source: a:136
Vetted: s
Judgment: g
Phenomena: wh questions
yeng la ka fo gaa
yeng  la   ka   fo  gaa
where FACT that you go.PERF
'where did you go?'
